{"type": "article", "id": 25139, "title": "秘密存钱罐", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-08T07:02:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 43, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607123111DqZbzXeILHdayOf7.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一个存钱罐，但它的投币口并不是真正用来投币的。需要将硬币卡在缝隙里旋转，然后将上面的盖子打开露出里面的罐子的空间，可以存放一些私密的物品。HIMITSU 在日语里是秘密的意思，它的确营造出了一点神秘气氛。设计师 Quentin de Coster 来自比利时，<a href=\"http://www.quentindecoster.com/\">这里是他的主页。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123109ST7qwvHdufVlM918.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071231104KO6eWmJYMv2hHz8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50642398\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123110jESmqNDaR8Ht9z4o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50642398\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123111mH1GU9ogBlVhaeqP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57230769\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}